[APC_0193.zip](https://github.com/mono/SkiaSharp/files/1616453/APC_0193.zip)

Sample images attached. The following sample code results in SKCodecOrigin.TopLeft, which is incorrect.

        private static SKBitmap Decode(string path, out SKCodecOrigin origin)
        {
            using (var stream = new SKFileStream(path))
            {
                using (var codec = SKCodec.Create(stream))
                {
                    // create the bitmap
                    var bitmap = new SKBitmap(codec.Info.Width, codec.Info.Height);

                    origin = codec.Origin;

                    return bitmap;
                }
            }
        }

Is this supported for dng files? The chrome browser is able to auto-orient them as expected.

> VS bug [#736302](https://devdiv.visualstudio.com/DevDiv/_workitems/edit/736302)
